{"tid":745533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人受災也不想吃的食物  受災也不想吃的農心辣味拉麵","createTime":"2018-07-17T00:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T02:11:35.000Z","uid":25345,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f312bfb2ad6a7c367d196ef7b5567f93edab1af3","tid":745533,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T00:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/_featured_image_8982303345b4c72ff69a37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F_featured_image_8982303345b4c72ff69a37.jpg&h=f8d682c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前西日本暴雨成災，有許多熱心人士捐贈物資到災區協助。但原來在捐贈物資當中，不是每一樣對災民來說是有用的。所以有災民就在Twitter上列出「受災地不需要的物品清單」，想不到有一樣食物是日本人不想要的&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1_9191222605b4c6d0d2f58c-1024x571.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F1_9191222605b4c6d0d2f58c-1024x571.jpg&h=94790b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那麼送即食麵對災民來說一定有用！可是根據「受災地不需要的物品清單」，原來日本人是不想收到辣味拉麵。相信辣味拉麵代表韓國出產的辛辣麵！<br />\n<br />\n在香港，辛辣麵是非常受歡迎的即食麵之一。可是日本人對於農心辛辣麵的反應就不太正面。<br />\n辛辣麵一直是韓國快餐美食必備。<br />\n<br />\n原來日本人不喜歡農心食品<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/503_6933317915b4c6ea89c704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F503_6933317915b4c6ea89c704.jpg&h=aea7cf9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這個即食麵世界裡，農心食品可謂佔一地位。與此同時，他們的辛辣麵醜聞亦相當多。每年都有網民或報導指拉麵混入了昆蟲、塑膠、異物和致癌物。所以日本人對於農心生產的食物信心大減。"},{"pid":"98cdd81e52f9460d3857cf7b9aeeb7a821926577","tid":745533,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"間屋比水沖走已經慘<br />\n仲要食d煲左成個字咬落去都係硬既麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b06b4166662ba2eac314d05541e9e14bf958aa","tid":745533,"uid":37389,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T00:44:43.000Z","msg":"有無咁深層次呀個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得根本係因為日本人唔食得辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6eb1ab7041fc5e87d4d820ca3c0e0933f2ee1f","tid":745533,"uid":20867,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T00:57:23.000Z","msg":"日本仔受災都仲講骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學下果D冇脊椎既民族la"},{"pid":"3781b6e026f5645551872f1bdc71b4966c6eb199","tid":745533,"uid":20072,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T00:59:28.000Z","msg":"咁簡擇既災民第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347c40a021322ec7a98f9316fbccdce811f3e524","tid":745533,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T01:08:27.000Z","msg":"農心辛拉麵有食物安全問題㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話人揀飲擇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://matome.naver.jp/odai/2143710847018653701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatome.naver.jp%2Fodai%2F2143710847018653701&d=a%2BxBxm13n%2FepoEKd0IwnLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=637201db\" target=\"_blank\">https://matome.naver.jp/odai/2143710847018653701</a><br />\n2008年 發現曱甴，公司死口否認<br />\n2011年 發現可致癌物質，"},{"pid":"c1ec2bb7fa9d3b46b947be97af585793e113787c","tid":745533,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"農心根本就係垃圾麵食，個辣味係用嚟掩蓋劣質材料同麵粉嘅噏味，係港豬先愛廢泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0050d5ed88dd81b331c9a5bf2811cb739ea0e56","tid":745533,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"韓國野本身就係垃圾啦"}]}